'Originally an iconic accessory of 90s rave culture, bucket hats are now the crowning glory of a well-rounded, practicality-focused closet,' says our senior menswear editor @lukejraymond. '@jw_anderson draws inspiration from its expressionist roots with an asymmetrical checked version that will lift even the simplest of looks.' Discover more clever fall accessories on #FARFETCH.

Photography by @giocorabi
Styling by @lukejraymond

#JWAnderson

node.text: 'My favorite sneaker of 2021 so far, hands down, is the @maniere_usa x #AirJordan3,’ says @mad.hartman, director of social at @stadiumgoods. 'A Ma Maniére founder @james.whitner’s elevated take on the Jordan 3, a classic silhouette, puts women front and center. The combination of Whitner’s personal connection — it was the first silhouette his mom purchased for him as a kid — with luxury details creates a one-of-a-kind collab.’ Find more sneaker collabs to know now on #FARFETCH.
